<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>My Website | About</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background: #f4f7fb;
            color: #333;
        }

        header {
            background: #0077ff;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px 50px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        nav a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-left: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #0077ff;
        }

        .card {
            background: white;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .card p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 15px;
            background: #0077ff;
            color: white;
            margin-top: 50px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <h2>MyWebsite</h2>
    <nav>
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="about">About</a>
    </nav>
</header>

<div class="container">
    <h1>About Me</h1>

    <div class="card">
        <p>
            Hello! I am a passionate developer who loves building clean and
            simple web applications. This website is created using only HTML
            and CSS to keep things lightweight and easy to understand.
        </p>

        <p>
            My goal is to learn, build, and grow every day. I enjoy working
            with backend development, AI, and full-stack projects.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>

<footer>
    © 2026 MyWebsite | About Page
</footer>

</body>
</html>
